case.name: Super Saiyan Transformation
case.description: Caulifla can change her hair and eye color on command. Cool huh? Also she gains a shining, golden aura around herself and grows in battle power immensely. But who cares about that sort of thing?

case.name: Super Orgasm
case.description: Looks like Caulifla turned Super Saiyan again. Must have felt pretty good, huh? This one doesn't stick around for as long however, it was kinda unintentional after all.
